He said he would murder a pedophile in cold blood without hesitation, even if it was me, or our parents. I told him murdering people would make him somewhat worse than a pedophile and he lost his mind, said I wasn't allowed near his children, I was defending pedophiles, I must be one, etc.

Then went right back to chatting.

When we stopped, I confronted him and demanded an apology. He apologized, hesitantly abd, in my opinion, insincerely. Told him "Someone who would say that to me is not my brother", and he got mad, doubled down, told me to fuck off. Got in a shouting match in front of his 3 year old daughter and both our parents. 

I told him in front of everyone that I don't consider him part of my family anymore.

Feeling pretty jumbled about it all, but I am sick of helping him when he's just a poisonous, unstable asshole. I'm so sick of tolerating him.

Just want to scream into the void with a shitty meme. Thank you for reading, if you still are. All men are my brothers, all women are my sisters, everyone between is my beloved sibling. I hope you all have an amazing day, week, year and life.

Front Page Edit: Thank you all for the concern, the advice, and the support. I want to reply to every comment but there are so many. I love you all, and I want the best for you all.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5z3W20y</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LordOfTheFattys]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Anyone else thinks this, or is it just me.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/a1eYcCA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/95I9IQ4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Haven't posted for a while but I think this world needs to grow up and do a reality check so we move on to a better society.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/a1eYcCA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[potato122]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Aarrggh! [OC]</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/gURX1Pm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oGMi39Q.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>No BONUS panel today, sorry folks!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/gURX1Pm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LitterboxComics]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>What it feels like to have the soul ripped out of you</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/zp4PKvd</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OEgHTZF.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/zp4PKvd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Potatoid]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Part 2 of recreating hairstyles from Star Wars!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/EBklmmW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eMq7IH3.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hfqjoFZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>There are no really clear shots of Leia's hair under Boushh's helmet, so I focused more on matching the front style and then created what I thought would work to keep long hair flat underneath. Something simple that someone could do quickly and by themselves, with just a *little* flair because duh.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EAurxfe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If y'all have a problem with the "rebranding" of this version of Leia, just know it's officially canon and I adore it wholeheartedly. Move along.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mZwyYVH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This was absolutely my favorite look of this video!! I may recreate it more often, albeit without the twine strands because those are a pain in the butt to take out.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5mWOcWH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And finally, one of Leia's other Endor hairstyles. She has a couple, but I really wanted to showcase the Ewoks handiwork a bit more so I chose this version over the infinity bun style ?
Hope you all have a fabulous day!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/EBklmmW</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GingerSnark]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Teacher for 17 years- Say her name, remember her face.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/uJp5SK0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dwwDeDv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A mother & wife who loved hiking. Died protecting her students.We will not forget. Fly High and rest sweetly.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/uJp5SK0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>“Pro-life,” my giant shiny American ass.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/C6RZ1vj</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yinriuL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/C6RZ1vj</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MoBullieMom]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sometimes; I make a meme for down votes.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/rw6DuBY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pPIRsNn.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/rw6DuBY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[autopsy4]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2c4dtIe</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PX8LHAX.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2c4dtIe</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DrDadJokes]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fucking hell, dude...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/X2pl5A1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/haxHF1U.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://im